            <section class="copy" data-chapter-top="3" data-chapter-bottom="3">
                <div>
                    <header>
                        <h3>Because His Holiday-Card List Is Probably Insane</h3>
                    </header>
                    <p>Sure, he plays up the misanthropic-maverick thing, but when it comes to family, Cage is entangled with no fewer than three Hollywood dynasties. Even his ex-cousins-in-law are somebodies!</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <div id="holiday-card" class="photo-scrollr">
                <div class="swipe"></div>
