            <section class="copy" data-chapter-top="4" data-chapter-bottom="4">
                <div>
                    <header>
                        <h3>Because He Was Nearly the Weirdest Superman of All Time</h3>
                    </header>
                    <p>And Neo. And the Wrestler. But what's better than Cage as the rainbow-suited, Jesus-haired Superman that got away?</p>
                    <aside class="mm-sidebar"></aside>
                    <div class="mm-inset">
                        <div>
                            <div class="img-container"><img src="http://www.gq.com/static/long-form/images/0.7.23/pages/nicolas_cage/inset/2.jpg" alt="Because He Was Nearly the Weirdest Superman of All Time" height="826" width="575"> <span><p><i class="illustrator"></i> Steve Brodner</p></span>
