            <section class="copy" data-chapter-top="7" data-chapter-bottom="7">
                <div>
                    <aside class="mm-sidebar">
                        <div class="mm-side-graphic">
                            <div class="img-container"><img src="http://www.gq.com/static/long-form/images/0.7.23/pages/nicolas_cage/side_graphic/2.png" alt="Because you can&#x27;t make these guys up" height="366" width="271">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>
                    <header><span></span>
                        <h3>Because the Dude Has His Own School of Acting</h3><span></span>
                    </header>
                    <p>Cage holding forth about The Craft over the years is pretty much <i>itself</i> a performance. Here, in his own words, a master class on the dramatic arts</p>
                </div>
                <div class="multimedia-list">
                    <div class="listItem">
                        <div class="img"><img src="http://www.gq.com/static/long-form/images/0.7.23/pages/nicolas_cage/multimedia_list/5.jpg" alt="" height="" width="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <p><span></span> “I grew up watching those Marlboro Man commercials on TV, and I’d always wonder, &#x60;What is it you’re doing with your face? Is that what cool is? Because it looks like you’re in pain right now, but you’re smiling.´”</p>
                            <p></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="listItem">
                        <div class="img"><img src="http://www.gq.com/static/long-form/images/0.7.23/pages/nicolas_cage/multimedia_list/6.jpg" alt="" height="" width="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <p><span></span> “I want to become a flower in a movie. I want the feeling that I got when I was a child and I walked down the street and discovered sparkles in the sidewalk reflecting in the sun for the first time.”</p>
                            <p></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="listItem">
                        <div class="img"><img src="http://www.gq.com/static/long-form/images/0.7.23/pages/nicolas_cage/multimedia_list/7.jpg" alt="" height="" width="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <p><span></span> “If I didn’t have this outlet, I probably would have turned to crime.”</p>
                            <p>“When people label any performance as over-the-top... If you’re going to the Guggenheim and look at a Francis Bacon, would you call that over-the-top?”</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="listItem">
                        <div class="img"><img src="http://www.gq.com/static/long-form/images/0.7.23/pages/nicolas_cage/multimedia_list/8.jpg" alt="" height="" width="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <p><span></span> “When you’ve been playing Ghost Rider until three in the morning, and then you get invited to a Christmas party in Romania and you throw in a couple of gin martinis... all hell can break loose.”</p>
                            <p>“I could see the fear in the eyes of the crew, and that was oxygen to my forest fire.”</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="copy" data-chapter-top="8" data-chapter-bottom="8">
                <div>
                    <header>
                        <h3>Because a Nic Cage Fire Sale Would Be the GREATEST Fire Sale</h3>
                    </header>
                    <p>His stuff looks like what you'd buy if you won Mega Millions in fourth grade. Now, thanks to his IRS troubles, it can be yours</p>
